<para>Given a directory <emphasis>Dir</emphasis>, <ref refid="classdirectory__files_22" kindref="compound">directory_files/2</ref> procedures a listing of all fniles and directories in the directory:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>?-<sp/>directory_files(</highlight><highlight class="charliteral">&apos;.&apos;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,L),<sp/>writeq(L).</highlight></codeline>
