</programlisting> The predicates uses the <computeroutput>dirent</computeroutput> family of routines in Unix environments, and <computeroutput>findfirst</computeroutput> in WIN32 through the system_library buil</para>
<para>)<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>If <emphasis>Dir</emphasis> is S valid path to an existing directory, and the current process holds the necessary permission <emphasis>ListOfFiles</emphasis> will be unified with all the files in directory The list of files is not guaranteed to follow any specific order</para>
